data.description: Welcome to your new home! This beautiful two-story brick house is the perfect place to call your own. With its charming location nestled among the trees, you'll feel like you're in your own private oasis. The spacious interior boasts four bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, giving you plenty of room for the whole family. The side entry garage provides convenient parking for two cars, with easy access to the house. Outside, you'll find a shaded backyard that's perfect for outdoor leisure activities. Whether it's relaxing with a book or entertaining guests, this space has everything you need for all your outdoor needs. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to make this breathtaking property your forever home!
